"3  (8-oz.) blocks mozzarella cheese","1  (8.5-oz.) jar sun-dried tomatoes, drained and halved","1/2 cup olive oil","3 tablespoons finely chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley","1 teaspoon garlic powder","1 teaspoon onion powder","1/2 teaspoon dried oregano","1/2 teaspoon Italian seasoning","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground pepper","  Garnish: flat-leaf parsley sprigs or fresh rosemary stems"